title: Myco-Myceliated Flac
description:
Debut Single "Myceliated" by psychedelic band Myco.

This song is about the effect fungus has on the universe as well as the human experience. The cover art for this single features a mushroom mandala as well as bitcoin qr code. Myco does not agree with how the entertainment industry works and feels that all art should be free. We do however accept bitcoin donations through scanning the qr code. Decentralize Everything!
